Invalid Number    |  1   |  1   |  1   |  1   |  1
Prospect          |  1   |  1   |  1   |  1   |  1
Interested        |  1   |  1   |  1   |  1   |  1
Didn't Connect    |  1   |  1   |  1   |  1   |  1
Lost Lead         | SKIP | SKIP | SKIP | SKIP | SKIP
Scheduled Call    | PASS until scheduled time
No Number         | SKIP — separate list

Day = 5:30 PM → 5:30 PM
